            <title>[MJAVADOC-115] getDocletPath does not return correct path</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-115</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;docletArtifacts is now never null, so really need an undefined check on each array entry. Further to that docletPath should always be appened, as its additional path info, at the moment its one or the other.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
